@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.exp(v0) + (wp.abs(v0 + 0.73) - v2))
    v2 = wp.cos((wp.abs(v0 + 0.34) / 0.90))
    v1 = ((0.01 + v2) - wp.exp(v1))
    v0 = ((v1 + (v1 + 0.05 * v1 + 0.84)) / wp.abs(0.46))
    data[tid] = v0
